<BR><BR>


Sea lions are also used as a clan animal in some Native American cultures. Tribes with Sea Lion Clans 
include the Tlingit and the Haida.
Sea Lion is used as a clan crest in some Northwest Coast tribes, and can sometimes 
be found carved on totem poles.


